Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ma tu sei il figlio di Heizo Hattori,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,il capo della polizia di Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:16.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho capito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:19.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho scoperto il trucco\N della stanza chiusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:19.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,E poi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.95,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan, che ti succede?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nel prossimo episodio di Conan...
